System Infomation Script: Write shell scripts to print system information.

#!/bin/bash
lscpu

Arithmetic Calculation: Write shell script to perform basic mathematical calculation.

#!/bin/bash

echo "Enter Number 1: "
read a

echo "Enter Number 2: "
read b

echo "Enter Operator: "
read op



Redirect Output: Use redirection operators to store the output of commands.

#!/bin/bash

echo "Enter a Command: "
read command

output=$($command)

echo "$command: $output" >> commands.md
